translate ru VargaPath5_1c47796a:
    # "Nearly a week had passed since Sarah learned of Marion's betrayal."
    ""

translate ru VargaPath5_879e252e:
    # "Sarah kept court as best she could, handing down her instructions to the different members of her council."
    ""

translate ru VargaPath5_b03a7dab:
    # "Her first goal was to understand the impacts of the uprising, and over the course of days, it had slowly become clear."
